          }
        },
        {
          "type": "problem",
          "problem": {
            "text": "If \\(\\mu(X)<\\infty\\), \\(f_n\\in L^1(\\mu)\\), and \\(f_n\\to f\\) uniformly, then \\(f\\in L^1(\\mu)\\) and \\(f_n\\to f\\) in the mean.",
