          }
        },
        {
          "type": "problem",
          "problem": {
            "text": "Prove the existence of the conditional expectation \\(E(f/\\mathcal F)\\) for functions \\(f\\in L^1(\\mu)\\), with respect to a \\(\\sigma\\)-algebra \\(\\mathcal F\\subset\\Sigma\\).",
